'''''en''''' is a [[Sindarin]] genitival article, usually meaning "of the". 

It is probably a combination of the determiner ''i'' and ''na'', "with, by".<ref>{{webcite|articleurl=http://www.jrrvf.com/hisweloke/sindar/online/sindar/dict-sd-en.html|articlename=Hiswelókë's Sindarin dictionary|author=[[Didier Willis]] (ed.)|website=[http://www.jrrvf.com/hisweloke/ Hiswelókë]}}</ref>
